    "Researchers may want to access raw data to analyze further, whereas applications for clinicians and teachers provide applications that can analyze the patients and students in clinical or teaching environments.",
    "Computational Discourse Analysis Application.",
    "Discourse provides multidomain data and information on language production, perception, planning, and cognition (35) (36) (37) (38).",
    "Thus, discourse can explain brain functioning and provide recommendations on whether there is evidence for a possible speech, language, and communication impairment.",
